item.title: CoreUI PRO Vue.js Admin Template v5.0.0-rc.1
item.description: We’re excited to release the CoreUI PRO Vue.js Admin Template v5.0.0-rc.1, dated March 23, 2024. This iteration of our template introduces a host of refinements and updates designed to streamline the development process, enhance the user interface, and ensure the template remains at the forefront of modern web development practices.
